text: Ærest on icenan æt brombrigce up andlang weges to hlidgeate.
Ðæt forð be mearce to cules felda.
Forð be gehrihtum gemære to stodleage.
Forð be mearce to ðæm ealdan falde.
A be hearpaðe to heafod stoccum.
Swa be hideburninga gemære on icenan.
<../images/tbar.gif>swa wið easton wordige þonan be rihtre mearce to ðæm gemærðornan.
To hearpaðe swa to tyrngeate wiðinnan ða æfisc to sceapwican.
Be rihton gemære to hige leage.
Swa on are dene forð be hagan on sceatte leage.
Swa mid streame ðæt hit cymð eft on brom bricge.
